data.description: A horse lovers property setup on 4.95 acres with 152 x 77 Sand Arena at an amazing price. Enjoy the seclusion and beautiful mountain views and only 8 minutes from downtown Emmett. 4 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom, 3472 Sq Ft home with sunken living room and private bonus room above the converted garage. New 30 year roof & newly remodeled kitchen. Sunken living room has a real wood burning fireplace. Owners Suite w/walk-in closet & dual sinks in ensuite. Property is set up for 3 seperate pastures, flood irrigation and a 22x12 lofing shed in 2nd pasture. A 4 stall 40x22 Pole barn with concrete floors & power. There is a built-in tack room in pole barn and has direct access to the sand arena for easy access to saddle and un-saddle horse(s). No HOA’s & No CCR’s complets this property. Buyer to verify all information.
